# ============================================================
# Connevia workspace — parent-level .gitignore
#
# The parent repo's remote (soreka/templateStarter) is PUBLIC.
# Anything agent-driven, operationally sensitive, or machine-local
# must NEVER be tracked here. Real code commits happen inside the
# two subrepos (connevia/ and connevia-server/), NOT at this level.
# ============================================================

# --- Agentic workflow (operational docs, agent configs, IDE-AI state) ---
STATUS.md
CLAUDE.md
.claude/
.cursor/
.windsurf*
WINDSURF_RULES.md

# --- Dependencies (should never be in git) ---
node_modules/

# --- Local build / dev state ---
.expo/
dist/
build/

# --- OS / editor cruft ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
